SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5934
A bill to amend 1972 PA 230, entitled
"Stille-DeRossett-Hale single state construction code act,"
(MCL 125.1501 to 125.1531) by adding section 11c.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 11c. For an application for a building permit or an
2 additional permit that an applicant submits to the department, if
3 the department fails to grant, in whole or in part, or deny the
4 application within the time periods described in section 11(1), the
5 department shall reimburse to the applicant the fee that the
6 applicant paid to the department under section 10.
7 Enacting section 1. This amendatory act does not take effect
8 unless all of the following bills of the 103rd Legislature are
9 enacted into law:
GSS H06480'26 (H-1) quad63

2
